description=Autonomous AI agent-as-OS for Android. v0.4.3: vendor-binder shim (camera + GPS + telephony) + streaming event bus + bg persistence + checkpoint resume + PCM record/playback/TTS. Installs peko-agent + peko-llm-daemon + tesseract into /system/bin with boot-time services and PekoOverlay + PekoSmsShim priv-apps. Multi-provider cloud chain, full autonomy stack, web UI on :8080, Telegram bot. Verified end-to-end on OnePlus 6T (fajita) / arm64 / LineageOS 20.
